Great Movie! I never heard of it, but my husband had seen it and it wasn't on Netflix, so I bought it and now I make all of my friends watch it!

Tommy Lee Jones delivers a remarkable performance. And Cate Blanchett appears in one of her most memorable roles in The Missing. These are two good westerns full of drama and action.  With all the perils of the Mexican/American border, these two movies put you at the edge of your seat. I love the Wild West landscapes portrayed here. Great landscapes! Very impressive. The Missing is in English/French and has optional English/French subtitles (full screen). The Three Burials of Melquiades Estrada is in English with optional English/Spanish/French subtitles (full screen/widescreen format). This is a  2 disc set. I highly recommend for those who enjoy westerns.
This is a great dvd with two great movies in my criteria TOMY LEE JONES in those films deliver great actuations and original talent, high recomended entertainement.

The Three Burials of Melquiades Estrada is awe-inspiring thanks to the almost unbelievable acting genius of Tommy Lee Jones. Also, the story line is highly engrossing from the start and only continues to get better and better until its credible and satisfying conclusion. An authentic gem of a movie for the most discriminating viewers. The added bonus of The Missing make this a DVD offer that can't be refused!
